Comment.val: /*Batchserver enabled process to report security transfers between same product definitions.*/
/*Only report products of which the porfolio value at transfer date is bigger than the given threshold.*/

SQL_STMT_U.val: select t.tr_transnummer, t.tr_symbool, k.kc_code_alfa, t.tr_aantal, be.be_aantal_cijfers_display, be.be_bi_nummer, t.tr_prijs_factor, t.tr_prijs_tr_mntsrt, t.tr_be_muntsoort, t.tr_boekdatum, t.tr_transdatum, t.tr_mut_gemaakt, pr.pr_productnaam, t.tr_rel1, t.tr_rel1_rek1, r1.re_openingsdatum "REL1_RE_OPENINGSDATUM", ppr1.ppr_productnummer "REL1_PRODUCTNUMMER", ppr1.ppr_volgnr_per_product "REL1_PRODUCTVOLGNR", ppr1.ppr_id "REL1_PPR_ID", ppr1.ppr_einddatum "REL1_EINDDATUM", t.tr_rel2, t.tr_rel2_rek1, r2.re_openingsdatum "REL2_RE_OPENINGSDATUM", ppr2.ppr_productnummer "REL2_PRODUCTNUMMER", ppr2.ppr_volgnr_per_product "REL1_PRODUCTVOLGNR", ppr2.ppr_id "REL2_PPR_ID", ppr2.ppr_einddatum "REL2_EINDDATUM" from transactions t inner join clienten c1 on c1.cl_nummer=t.tr_rel1 and c1.cl_relatie_type=1 inner join clienten c2 on c2.cl_nummer=t.tr_rel2 and c2.cl_relatie_type=1 inner join rekeningen r1 on r1.re_nummer=t.tr_rel1 and r1.re_rekening = t.tr_rel1_rek1 and r1.re_soort =t.tr_rel1_rek1_soort and r1.re_muntsoort = ' ' inner join rekeningen r2 on r2.re_nummer=t.tr_rel2 and r2.re_rekening = t.tr_rel2_rek1 and r2.re_soort =t.tr_rel2_rek1_soort and r2.re_muntsoort = ' ' inner join rekeningen_per_product rp1 on rp1.rpp_relatienummer=t.tr_rel1 and rp1.rpp_rekening_nummer = t.tr_rel1_rek1 and rp1.rpp_rekeningsoort =t.tr_rel1_rek1_soort and rp1.rpp_valuta = ' ' inner join producten pr on pr.pr_productnummer = rp1.rpp_productnummer inner join rekeningen_per_product rp2 on rp2.rpp_relatienummer=t.tr_rel2 and rp2.rpp_rekening_nummer = t.tr_rel2_rek1 and rp2.rpp_rekeningsoort =t.tr_rel2_rek1_soort and rp2.rpp_valuta = ' ' and rp2.rpp_productnummer=rp1.rpp_productnummer inner join producten_per_relatie ppr1 on ppr1.ppr_relatienummer=t.tr_rel1 and ppr1.ppr_productnummer=rp1.rpp_productnummer and ppr1.ppr_volgnr_per_product=rp1.rpp_volgnr_per_product inner join producten_per_relatie ppr2 on ppr2.ppr_relatienummer=t.tr_rel2 and ppr2.ppr_productnummer=rp2.rpp_productnummer and ppr2.ppr_volgnr_per_product=rp2.rpp_volgnr_per_product and ppr2.ppr_id<>ppr1.ppr_id left outer join koerskodes k on k.kc_symbool=t.tr_symbool and k.kc_optietype=t.tr_optietype and k.kc_expiratiedatum=t.tr_expiratiedatum and k.kc_exerciseprijs=t.tr_exerciseprijs and k.kc_leverancier= ~1 inner join beleggingsinstrument be on be.be_symbool=t.tr_symbool and be.be_optietype=t.tr_optietype and be.be_expiratiedatum=t.tr_expiratiedatum and be.be_exerciseprijs=t.tr_exerciseprijs where r2.re_openingsdatum>='20201030' and t.tr_transnummer>0 and t.tr_boekdatum between ~2 and ~3 and t.tr_indicatie = 'O' order by t.tr_transnummer
